h1. mvcGroupManager

h2. Purpose

Property that points to the MVCGroupManager instance.

h2. Description

The @MVCGroupManager@ is responsible for keeping the configuration for all MVC groups as well as instantiating and initializing them. This class relies on @MVCGroupConfiguration@ and @MVCGroup@ to manage groups.

@MVCGroupConfiguration@ holds the group configuration as expressed in @Application.groovy@ or by [addons|guide:addons]. @MVCGroup@ points to an instantiated group.